                    <comment id="12704675" author="jukkaz" created="Thu, 30 Apr 2009 16:51:45 +0100"  >Another somewhat related issue: the LuceneQueryFactoryImpl.create(FullTextSearchImpl) method tries to parse the full text search expression, but with the JCR 2.0 API the expression is a StaticOperand instead of a String.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
For now I added a simple toString() call to convert the StaticOperand to something that can be parsed, but there is probably a better way to do this.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
See line 209 in LuceneQueryFactoryImpl.java for the details.</comment>
